Daga: gt7469a@prism.gatech.EDU (Brian R. Landmann) Subject: Torre: Mummunan kocin?
Joe Torre ya kasance mafi mũnin kocin a baseball.
Ga duk wanda ya ba su gani ranar Lahadi game,
Tare da dama hander pitching ya yanke shawarar da ya benci Lankform, a bar bangaren hitter da wasa Jordan da kuma gilkey, duka daidai handers.
Daga baya, a ta tara inning tare da kwasfansu ɗora Kwatancen da biyu sabani ya sanya lankford, a 300 hitter da iko a matsayin tsunkule zo ta biyu da kuma yana amfani da Luis Alicea, a 250 hitter ba tare da wani iko a matsayin tsunkule hitter.
Abin da Jahannama ne ya tunanin.
Tun da farko a wasan a wata hira game da samun Mark yaƙi ya karrama ya yi sharhi yadda m da Kadina kasance a samu yaƙi ya karrama da cewa yaƙi ya karrama zai zama yau da kullum ko da yake wannan nufi cewa Gilkey za a cuce, Amma torre ya ce ya na son zuwa Gilkey kashe benci.
Gilkey buga a kan 300 a bara, abin da bã ya yi don fara, The Guy za a fara a kan mafi kowane tawagar a league.
Bugu da ƙari kuma, a lahadi wasan a lokacin da lankford aka jefa fita a farantin, The Replay nuna Bucky lan wasa na uku tushe kocin neman saukar da line kuma waving lankford gida,
Ba zan iya daukar wannan babu kuma
